      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个物流追踪号生成后的完整处理流程。核心是从聚合根产生事件开始，经过事件存储、反应器，最终到副作用执行。我想先确认参与者：聚合（Aggregate）、事件存储（Event Store）、反应器（Reactor）、队列（Queue）、队列工作者（Queue Worker）和副作用服务（Side Effect）。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白，六个参与者。我按时间顺序排列，从左到右：Aggregate → Event Store → Reactor → Queue → Queue Worker → Side Effect。这样符合事件流向吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对的。第一步是聚合把事件存到Event Store，然后Event Store要把事件分派给Reactor。Reactor收到后推送任务到Queue，Queue Worker取出来处理，最后去执行Side Effect。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect",
        "Store Event",
        "Dispatch Event",
        "Push Job",
        "Process Job",
        "Execute Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加这五步消息流：A到E的Store Event，E到R的Dispatch Event，R到Q的Push Job，Q到W的Process Job，以及W到S的Execute Side Effect。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Store Event",
        "Dispatch Event",
        "Push Job",
        "Process Job",
        "Execute Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Side Effect执行完需要处理两种结果。成功的话，返回成功状态，Queue Worker要把任务标记为已完成；失败的话，返回失败，然后要触发重试机制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Side Effect",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue",
        "Return Success",
